.codex/
# .claude/ is a mixed dir: agents/ is committed (shared release-manager etc.),
# personal state (data/, logs/, settings.local.json, transcripts) is not.
# Re-including a path requires its parents to remain un-excluded, so list the
# personal paths explicitly instead of excluding the whole dir.
.claude/data/
.claude/logs/
.claude/transcripts/
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/projects/
.claude/cache/
.pytest_cache/
.github/.ace-version.json
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.sqlite3
*.db
.DS_Store
node_modules/
dist/
coverage/
*.log
